                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-08-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">讨论艺术性多于技巧，不过这样看来，罗兰巴特也算个通才了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

